{% set description %}
The modal container's coloring theme can be adjusted by the  <code>theme</code> prop. The default is set to <code>xlight</code>.
{% endset %}

{% set notes %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li>The <code>none</code> prop makes the modal container transparent.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>The <code>xlight</code>, <code>light</code>, <code>dark</code>, and <code>xdark</code> props adds the respective theme to the modal container.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>The <code>theme</code> prop only applies to viewports equal to or above the small breakpoint (~600px).</bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
{% endset %}

{% set demo %}
